<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>The original Motor Toon Grand Prix was only released in Japan, a creative racer that never really eventuated due to lacking gameplay. Motor Toon GP 2 is an imaginative cartoony roller coaster race set in a number of wacky worlds with strong similarities between a mix of Mario Kart and Wipeout.
                  <br><br>Sony's MotorToon Grand Prix 2 takes racing into furistic warped world of cartoon images and bright lights. Visually the game is spectacular taking players through such locations as haunted castles, glass roads, through volcanoes and other cartoony locations. Motor Toon GP2 features more than ten tracks and eight racers each with different skills and abilities.
                  <br><br>Unlike many of other titles of cute and childish nature, Motor Toon GP2 is not for the faint hearted and includes five difficulties levels. Motor Toon Grand Prix 2 also takes advantage of Sony's link up feature and a second disc link up copy of the game is included.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>THE WACKIEST RACE EVER!
                  <br>A wild and zany ride in a topsy-turvy grand prix!
                  <br><br>* Race 10 fantastical, fun-filled tracks.
                  <br>* Stunning, Colorful Animation!
                  <br>* Lob tons of wacky weapons.
                  <br>* Ride 8 racy roadsters.
                  <br>* Master 32 ton weights, oil cans, fire balls and even a crazy mushroom!
                  <br>* Hidden bonus levels!
                  <br>* Loads of fun for everyone!
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>3D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Racing & Fantasy themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

